    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"环 is fundamental in Chinese concepts of wholeness and completion. In feng shui and traditional\nChinese philosophy, circular shapes (环形) represent harmony and completeness. 环境 (environment)\nemphasizes how surroundings completely encircle and influence us. The ring shape symbolizes eternal\ncycles and continuity in Chinese culture."}],"type":"paragraph"}
